import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
from sklearn.ensemble import RandomForestRegressor
from sklearn.preprocessing import LabelEncoder
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import seaborn as sns

df = pd.read_csv("/path/to/Gly-data y1 copy.csv")

def clean_target(val):
    if str(val).strip() in ['No Reaction', 'Trace', 'Later']:
        return 0.01
    try:
        return float(val)
    except:
        return np.nan

df['y1'] = df['y1'].apply(clean_target)
df = df.dropna(subset=['y1'])

target_col = 'y1'
feature_cols = [col for col in df.columns if col.startswith('x')]  # x1 to x23
X = df[feature_cols]
y = df[target_col]

for col in X.select_dtypes(include=['object', 'category']):
    X[col] = LabelEncoder().fit_transform(X[col].astype(str))

model = RandomForestRegressor(n_estimators=200, random_state=42)
model.fit(X, y)

importances = model.feature_importances_
importance_df = pd.DataFrame({
    'Feature': feature_cols,
    'Importance': importances
}).sort_values(by='Importance', ascending=False).reset_index(drop=True)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.ticker as mticker
import matplotlib.font_manager as fm

font_path = fm.findSystemFonts(fontpaths=None, fontext='ttf')
for font in font_path:
    if 'arial' in font.lower():
        fm.fontManager.addfont(font)
plt.rcParams['font.family'] = 'Arial'

feature_importance_df = pd.DataFrame({
    'Feature': [
        'xxx'
    ],
    'Importance': [
        xxx
    ]
})

feature_importance_df = feature_importance_df.sort_values(by='Importance', ascending=False)

plot_width = 8  
plot_height = 6  
font_size_title = 18
font_size_labels = 14
font_size_ticks = 12

fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(plot_width, plot_height), dpi=800)

colors = sns.color_palette("viridis", len(feature_importance_df))

cmap = plt.get_cmap('viridis')

bars = ax.barh(feature_importance_df['Feature'], feature_importance_df['Importance'], color=colors)

ax.invert_yaxis()

ax.spines['top'].set_visible(False)
ax.spines['right'].set_visible(False)

for bar in bars:
    width = bar.get_width()
    label_position = width - 5 if width > 10 else width + 1  
    ax.text(label_position, bar.get_y() + bar.get_height()/2,
            f'{width:.2f}%',
            ha='center' if width > 10 else 'left', va='center',
            fontsize=font_size_ticks, color='white' if width > 10 else 'black')

ax.set_xlabel('Importance Score (%)', fontsize=font_size_labels, labelpad=12, fontweight='bold')
ax.set_ylabel('Features', fontsize=font_size_labels, labelpad=12, fontweight='bold')

ax.tick_params(axis='both', which='major', labelsize=font_size_ticks, length=5, width=1)

ax.set_xlim(0, feature_importance_df['Importance'].max() + 5)

ax.xaxis.grid(False)
ax.yaxis.grid(False)

plt.tight_layout()

plt.show()

plt.savefig('feature_importance_plot.png', dpi=800, bbox_inches='tight')

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.font_manager as fm

font_paths = fm.findSystemFonts(fontpaths=None, fontext='ttf')
for font in font_paths:
    if 'arial' in font.lower():
        fm.fontManager.addfont(font)
plt.rcParams['font.family'] = 'Arial'

feature_importance_df = pd.DataFrame({
    'Feature': [
        'xxx'
    ],
    'Importance': [
        xxx
    ]
})


donor_color = 'mediumseagreen'
acceptor_color = 'green'
other_color = 'yellowgreen'
efi_color = 'limegreen'  

ordered_features = donor_features + acceptor_features + other_features + efi_feature

feature_importance_df = feature_importance_df.set_index('Feature').loc[ordered_features].reset_index()

def categorize_feature(f):
    if f in donor_features:
        return 'Donor'
    elif f in acceptor_features:
        return 'Acceptor'
    elif f in other_features:
        return 'Other'
    elif f in efi_feature:
        return 'EFI'
    else:
        return 'Unknown'

feature_importance_df['Category'] = feature_importance_df['Feature'].apply(categorize_feature)

category_order = ['Acceptor', 'Donor', 'Other', 'EFI']
feature_importance_df['Category'] = pd.Categorical(feature_importance_df['Category'], categories=category_order, ordered=True)
feature_importance_df = feature_importance_df.sort_values(by=['Category', 'Importance'], ascending=[True, False])

color_map = {
    **{feat: donor_color for feat in donor_features},
    **{feat: acceptor_color for feat in acceptor_features},
    **{feat: other_color for feat in other_features},
    **{feat: efi_color for feat in efi_feature}
}
colors = [color_map[feat] for feat in feature_importance_df['Feature']]

fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(6, 4), dpi=800)

bar_height = 0.8
bars = ax.barh(feature_importance_df['Feature'], feature_importance_df['Importance'], 
               color=colors, edgecolor=bar_edge_color, height=bar_height)

for bar, imp in zip(bars, feature_importance_df['Importance']):
    label = f"{imp:.1f}%" if imp % 1 != 0 else f"{int(imp)}%"
    plt.text(bar.get_width() + 0.5, bar.get_y() + bar.get_height()/2, 
             label, va="center", fontsize=8, fontweight="normal", color="black")

ax.set_xlabel("Importance (% α-selectivity)", fontsize=11, fontweight="bold", labelpad=6)
ax.set_ylabel("Features", fontsize=12, fontweight="bold")
ax.set_xlim(0, 25)

ax.spines['bottom'].set_position(('data', 14.8))  

ax.set_yticklabels(feature_importance_df['Feature'], fontsize=8, rotation=45, ha='right')

ax.axhline(14.8, color='black', lw=0.9) 
ax.axvline(0.01, color='black', lw=0.9) 

ax.set_yticklabels(feature_importance_df['Feature'], fontsize=8, rotation=0, ha='right')


plt.text(16.9, 2.5, "Alcohol effect: 46%", fontsize=9, color=acceptor_color, fontweight="normal")
plt.text(20.5, 7.7, "Glycosylating\nagent effect: 43%", fontsize=9, color=donor_color, fontweight="normal", ha='center')
plt.text(18.5, 12.5, "Environmental\n   effect: 12%", fontsize=9, color=other_color, fontweight="normal")

plt.annotate("", xy=(24, 0.05), xytext=(24, 4.2), arrowprops=dict(arrowstyle="<->", color=acceptor_color, lw=1.8))
plt.annotate("", xy=(24, 4.3), xytext=(24, 9.8), arrowprops=dict(arrowstyle="<->", color=donor_color, lw=1.8))
plt.annotate("", xy=(24, 14), xytext=(24, 10), arrowprops=dict(arrowstyle="<->", color=other_color, lw=1.8))

plt.gca().invert_yaxis()
plt.box(False)

plt.tight_layout()
save_path = '/path/to/feature_importance_plot.png'
plt.savefig(save_path, dpi=800, bbox_inches='tight')

plt.show()
